<item>
            <title>[LU-16097] Mitigate the affect from pre-allocated quota after the quota is over limit</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16097</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There could be some pre-acquired quota space at some MDTs or OSTs after the quota&lt;br/&gt;
for some quota ID is over limit, these quota (file quota or block quota) can still be used&lt;br/&gt;
when creating files in these MDTs (file quota) or writing data into files (block quota),&lt;br/&gt;
these quota space should be reclaimed in such case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
